Monologue: Donald Trump stumps em all. From immigration to racism, he seems like teflon. Jeb ignores Trump, loves sharknado.

Party panel: GAVIN MCCINES, KAYLEIGH McENANY, and  MELISSA FRANCIS . Barrack Obama dives into the 2016 fight. - Draft Joe Biden into the race. "Ridin' with Biden". Will he run or wont he?

Our panel returns. More email problems for Hillary Clinton. - More Hillary news. She promises to install 5 million solar panels by the end of her first term.

PENN JILLETTE is in studio to talk about a recent spat with Donald Trump, and his new show broadway show.

The panel reteurns. Trump bans newspaper for hostile editorial.  - Airline offers massages.

Kennedy loves having food in studio so tonight she's got a few  milkshakes from Sonic. She interviews MACKENZIE GIBCON, Sonic's own senior director of culinary innovation.
